report.RowPanel_HQEP_beforePrint_grp2init = function() {
   if(report.curPrintGrpId == $.执行计划标识){
    report.curOrdIdx++;
  }else{
    report.curPrintGrpId = $.执行计划标识;
    if($.item.length < 5){
      report.curOrdTotalIdx = 1;
    }else if($.item.length % 5 == 0){
         report.curOrdTotalIdx = $.item.length / 5;
    }else{
       report.curOrdTotalIdx= Number(($.item.length / 5).toFixed(0)) + 1;
    }

    report.curOrdIdx = 1;
  }

report.RowPanel_8yWe_beforePrint_detail_row = function() {
  report.ytzl  = 0;
  //report.curPatIdx = $.row + 1;
  report.yzsm = $.嘱托;
  let date = new Date(parseInt($.用药计划列表[0].计划执行时间));
  let m = date.getMonth();
  let d = date.getDate();
  if(m + 1 < 10){
    m = "0" + (date.getMonth() + 1);
  }
  if(d + 1 < 10){
    d = "0" + date.getDate()
  }
  report.yyrq =  date.getFullYear() + "" + m + "" +  d;
  report.fyks = $.发药药房名称;
  report.qr = $.住院打印条码;
  report.ypbz = $.备注;
  for(let obj of $.item){
    // 289848825055571982 ml ，累加
    if(obj.住院发药剂量单位代码 == '289848825055571982'){
        report.ytzl = report.ytzl + Number(obj.发药剂量);
    }
  }
}
